name: Archer
description:
Archer is the First playable character of the Tezos Defenders project!

The archer has a base health of 80
Base damage of 12

His basic attack fires a arrow at your cursor location
His ability fires 2 additional arrows and also make your arrows pierce and bounce to a nearby target up to 2 additional times

-----------------------------

Tezos Defenders is a a collection of playable characters in a top down game in which you have to survive and kill skeletons, while making your character more powerful with items that you'll get from the enemies, chests and statues

The game will expand as more characters are launched
New characters will feature a new version of the game, updated, hotfixed and with more content

-----------------------------

The games / characters will always be free to play in the site, but you'll can collect it to have in your collection and also to support the Artist who created the game (who always have dreamed of making a living out of giving life to the universes in my head). Thank you for playing, thank for being part of it!

With love -
